tr.com.turkcellteknoloji.turkcellupdater
Class Properties

java.lang.Object
  tr.com.turkcellteknoloji.turkcellupdater.Properties

public class Properties
extends Object

Represents Device and application properties. Following property values are automatically retrieved:

  • KEY_APP_INSTALLER_PACKAGE_NAME
  • KEY_APP_PACKAGE_NAME
  • KEY_APP_VERSION_CODE
  • KEY_APP_VERSION_NAME
  • KEY_DEVICE_API_LEVEL
  • KEY_DEVICE_BRAND
  • KEY_DEVICE_IS_TABLET
  • KEY_DEVICE_LANGUAGE
  • KEY_DEVICE_MCC
  • KEY_DEVICE_MNC
  • KEY_DEVICE_MODEL
  • KEY_DEVICE_PRODUCT

These values can be overrided by calling setValue(String, String) method. Also it is possible to introduce new key-value pairs using KEY_COSTUM_PREFIX.

Author:
Ugur Ozmen

KEY_DEVICE_IS_TABLET

public static final String KEY_DEVICE_IS_TABLET
"true" if devices is a tablet, otherwise "false". Since there is no clear evidence to determine if an Android device is tablet or not, devices with minimum screen size wider than 600 dpi are considered as tablets.
Example values: "true", "false".
